{"_path":"/resident/r041","_dir":"resident","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"煙蒂如何回收？","description":null,"image":"/images/resident/r040-11.png","sequence":40,"category":"社區營造","place":"A7重劃區","author":"社區網站","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2025 "},{"name":"og:title","content":"社區網站-地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-08-04T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"煙蒂如何回收"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"煙蒂如何回收？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區 許多社區已將向市府申請成為禁菸社區。 隱君子只能在路邊抽菸, 路旁的下水道孔成了公共煙灰缸。 路邊隨意丟棄的煙蒂成為主要拉圾來源。 居民們是否也想有一個沒有煙蒂的乾淨環境呢？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"摘錄國外的做法, 希望有市府官員/民意代表 能找出桃園的煙蒂治理辦法！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r041-01.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r041-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"他山之石-加拿大蒙特婁的煙蒂回收作業"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"他山之石 - 加拿大蒙特婁的煙蒂回收作業"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在蒙特婁，有多項旨在回收菸蒂的舉措，以應對這類廢棄物對環境造成的影響。該市已實施一項名為 Mégot Zéro 的計畫，其中包括安裝公共菸灰缸，並與非營利組織 Sollicité 合作，負責收集和回收菸蒂。 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"收集到的菸蒂會被進一步處理，將塑膠濾嘴回收，而菸草和菸紙則進行堆肥"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以下是蒙特婁菸蒂回收工作的詳細介紹："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://westmount.org/en/news/waste-and-sustainability/recycling-cigarette-butts-with-the-megot-zero-programme"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mégot Zéro 計畫"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n這項計畫由 Sollicité 組織主導，主要負責從公共場所收集和回收菸蒂。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://westmount.org/en/news/waste-and-sustainability/recycling-cigarette-butts-with-the-megot-zero-programme"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公共菸灰缸"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n市府已在多個地點，包括繁忙的街道和商業區附近，安裝了大量的菸灰缸，為吸菸者提供指定的丟棄點。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.ctvnews.ca/montreal/article/montreal-group-collects-cigarette-butts-for-recycling/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"回收過程"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n收集到的菸蒂會被送到回收廠，將塑膠濾嘴分離並回收製成新產品，而菸草和菸紙部分則進行堆肥。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.terracycle.com/en-CA/brigade_groups/unsmoke-groups-ca"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"與 TerraCycle"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 的合作夥伴關係"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n蒙特婁還與專門回收難以回收廢棄物的公司 TerraCycle 合作，來處理收集到的菸蒂。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.ctvnews.ca/montreal/article/montreal-group-collects-cigarette-butts-for-recycling/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"社區參與"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nSAESEM 等組織也積極參與推廣菸蒂回收，透過教育宣導活動和安裝收集箱來響應。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ecoquartierpetermcgill.org/en/crowdfunding-campaign-to-recycle-cigarette-butts/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"與 Éco-quartier"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 的合作"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nÉco-quartier Peter-McGill 也參與了 Mégot Zéro 計畫，提供公共菸灰缸並與其他 Éco-quartier 合作擴大該計畫。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"重視預防 "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n蒙特婁市府也積極透過公眾宣導活動和社群媒體，強調隨意亂丟菸蒂的負面環境影響，以阻止亂丟菸蒂的行為。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"煙蒂如何回收","depth":2,"text":"煙蒂如何回收？","children":[{"id":"他山之石-加拿大蒙特婁的煙蒂回收作業","depth":3,"text":"他山之石 - 加拿大蒙特婁的煙蒂回收作業"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:resident:r041.md","_source":"content","_file":"resident/r041.md","_extension":"md"}